{
  "stem": "12413.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We jump out to another train which took us to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Buchenwald is five miles from Weimar, located in Thuringen state on Ettersberg heights-- hills-- surrounded by wooded area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A real concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When I learned later the span of life [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was between 30 and 45 days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When we arrived to this place, and I saw Buchenwald [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we crossed the gate, I saw the inscription.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Then I understood the substance of human nature.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That people-- not everybody's good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Not everybody's mean.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But people to people, somehow-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there is a Latin saying, which says, homini-- homini homini lupus-- homo homini lupus.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It means, 'a human being to human being is a wolf.' This was said in ancient Rome, thousands of years ago.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But probably it was true in modern times too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Me, my first question was-- there was a guy with a triangle-- a red triangle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was a former Communist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was one of the guys who was watching, you know, the people, you know, taking them to the bath house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I asked him the first question, if there is a gas chamber in this place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was my first question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He said to me, there is no gas chamber in this place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There is a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the dead bodies are burned after they die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "People die, he said to me, mostly from starvation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This was my question.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This was the end of the dialogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I spoke to him in German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He was French, or Belgian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went to this bath house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It looked to me very suspicious.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
